{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now my name was Jan Migon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those were the papers from which I had my name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jan, J-A-N, Migon-- Migon, M-I-G-O-N.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As time went on, I got used more and more to that name, and I tried as much as possible to convince myself that that's my real name, you know, so that in a normal day-to-day situation when you encounter people, I would be able to face questions or interrogations without panicking, and just naturally say that this is my name.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Part of that, also to try to erase from memory my whole childhood, my whole being, my-- my whole existence prior to that, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because indeed, every once in a while, I had to undergo strange tests.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was able to pass the tests.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, the German suddenly announced that every young boy, age of 18, 19, or 20-- I forgot exactly, and I was in that category at that point with my papers-- has to register with the Labor Department.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I registered, I listened to other people talking and all that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was clear that those people will be sent to Germany to work, build some fortifications or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They weren't treated like Jews, like slave laborers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were more treated like recruits in the army, except they wouldn't be in the-- in-- in the army-- but in the labor battalion.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I befriended one of the clerks there who was in charge of that registration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I talked with him and all that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally I asked him, can you help me, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And out of that conversation, he gave me a tip.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Try to do this and that, and gave me back my form which I filled out.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
